Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The keys came knocking at Chromium's door,
"We're from the terminal!" — sixty or more.
kRawKeyDown, kChar, the protocol's dance,
But Enter still freezes — needs one more chance.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
